data.description: Charming ranch-style home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a few fresh cosmetic updates Co new countertops, new flooring, new paint and new lighting. This home is situated in the serene, tranquil, suburban neighborhood in the Lithonia/Stonecrest area. This residence offers a peaceful retreat while still being conveniently close to local amenities, errands, and major highways. Meticulously maintained, this adorable home exudes charm and features a bright and airy living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The galley kitchen, adorned with new granite countertops, seamlessly connects to the living and dining room space, providing an open and spacious feel. Step outside to the expansive backyard, complete with a deck perfect for entertaining and enjoying outdoor gatherings. Take advantage of the easy access to nearby amenities, restaurants, shopping, and a lively community. This residence combines modern updates with a cozy ambiance, making it an ideal place to call home.
